Title: Timerange buttons for downtimes can now be configured
Level: 1
Component: wato
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.4.0i1
Date: 1460101816
Class: feature

The dialog to set a downtime currently offers 5 buttons to quickly set a downtime: 2 hours, today,
this week, this month and this year.
Now one can add additional ranges or replace the current ones. The configuration can be found under
Globals Settings->Custom Downtime Timeranges
